data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming residence boasts fresh exterior paint and brand-new laminate flooring, complete with modern baseboards, throughout the lower level. Prepare for a seamless and comfortable move-in experience with everything provided. Inside, you'll discover two distinct living areas, ensuring ample space for hosting gatherings. For those in need of a dedicated office space, look no further – there's a convenient office area tucked away in the two-car garage. This four-bedroom gem offers spacious living on the upper level, ensuring privacy and tranquility. The master bedroom is a true retreat with a generous walk-in closet featuring built-in shelving – perfect for keeping your wardrobe organized. The kitchen has been recently updated with sleek white cabinets and all brand-new appliances, ensuring a modern and efficient cooking experience. It even includes a washer and dryer upstairs for your convenience. Designed with functionality in mind, it features easily accessible garbage and recycling bins. Say goodbye to the hassles of gas-powered lawn equipment, as this home comes with an electric mower, weed eater, and shears, making lawn maintenance a breeze. But that's not all – this delightful home is situated just across the street from a picturesque creek and features a charming bike trail nearby. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this house your new home.
